author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! Nexus mods recently removed a mod for Oblivion's remaster that allowed you to replace text in the game with "Male/Female", Nexus removed this mod and created a multi day backlash and I couldn't stop hearing about it. I decided to look into it. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: Massive Nexus Mods Controversy Just Happened...
